data.description: Views forever from this hilltop home. This desirable country setting in West Auburn is in the heart of the wine trail and just a few minutes from Highway 49.  It needs some love but could be a gorgeous home for your family. The property is fenced, crossed fenced and has irrigation water available. There's lots of room for the kids, pets, livestock a garden and an orchard. The master suite has access to the deck with those great views. The indoor laundry/mud room offers extra storage. Don't miss the tool sheds out back. Enjoy the sunsets with a nice glass of wine on the large back deck. Come take a look.
